Text: V - 4rnA - 4rnrnStarts good, image quality is OK but in the first part of the movie you have seats in the way, who ever did this needs to turn the auto focus off on the cam, a good part of the middle and ending are out of focus as the camera finds it hard to find something to focus on, you also get people standing up in the audience a few times, as for sound it jumps from being good to muffled with loads of bass a few times as well. other than that, its how a cam usually sounds, slight echo and slightly tinny. rnrnVerdict, wait for a better quality copyrnrn- if you like it, support the movies, go cinema after or buy the DVD when available and add it to your collection.
